{"created":"2025-10-27T21:54:11.129-0400","author":"Stanislav Gordiienko","body":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"557058:1bb6163b-b0ba-4dfc-8892-544386c08519","text":"@Wei (Irene) Jiang","accessLevel":"","localId":"9ac4adab-9e64-446a-9c12-cfec3dec2a26"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"557058:7dfe389b-baf9-4c02-bcff-902031c775f2","text":"@Qingling Dong","accessLevel":"","localId":"fe9a759d-ef75-4113-af00-1f8ee1fa4507"}},{"type":"text","text":" I propose that we move this feature to Q2 candidate. Would you have any concerns?"}]}]}
{"created":"2025-10-28T14:41:06.782-0400","author":"Stanislav Gordiienko","body":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"557058:1bb6163b-b0ba-4dfc-8892-544386c08519","text":"@Wei (Irene) Jiang","accessLevel":"","localId":"37ad1fed-cb5c-4c3a-a9fa-6e29dbafe466"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"557058:7dfe389b-baf9-4c02-bcff-902031c775f2","text":"@Qingling Dong","accessLevel":"","localId":"4b4b35c1-6348-4e27-b454-7d412338ffc2"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"We have two more cases ("},{"type":"text","text":"CGWS-3281","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://strategyagile.atlassian.net/browse/CGWS-3281"}}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","text":"BCVE2374","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://strategyagile.atlassian.net/browse/BCVE-2374"}}]},{"type":"text","text":") that are not directly, but are related to the topic of report exports to excel (in both WS and Library). We can either track them under the same feature or have two separate ones. I strongly encourage to keep it as one to ensure that scope doesn’t get cut. Below are brief details of these cases."},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"In WS we don’t have any advanced settings for Excel exports of the report. "}]},{"type":"mediaSingle","attrs":{"width":1021,"widthType":"pixel","layout":"align-start"},"content":[{"type":"media","attrs":{"type":"file","id":"c1a8577d-6ffc-4198-b4f6-c6a6ce25542a","alt":"image-20251028-182922.png","collection":"","height":865,"width":1380}}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oddly, we actually have report title option at the application level and Library."},{"type":"hardBreak"}]},{"type":"mediaSingle","attrs":{"width":864,"widthType":"pixel","layout":"align-start"},"content":[{"type":"media","attrs":{"type":"file","id":"2ccb45f2-1433-4aa1-a62a-fdf321b44cb1","alt":"image-20251028-183231.png","collection":"","height":510,"width":864}}]},{"type":"mediaSingle","attrs":{"width":647,"widthType":"pixel","layout":"align-start"},"content":[{"type":"media","attrs":{"type":"file","id":"42530add-5096-4227-885b-56f38d5247e7","alt":"image-20251028-183858.png","collection":"","height":500,"width":647}}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So we should consider these advanced options to be added to WS as well for a consistent experience."},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"Therefore, proposed scope to this feature is:"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"-export report in authoring mode (including WS, not just Library)"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"-export with advanced options such as report title and filters (report and view)"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"In terms of priority, we should first focus on Report View filters becoming accessible and OOTB feature and then consider these enhancements (potentially mid 2026)."},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"Do you have any concern?"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"cc: "},{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"557058:1fe9d8ca-645f-4c2e-894d-130e1af8e10d","text":"@Alejandro Olvera Velasco","accessLevel":"","localId":"08da0171-4919-4ab8-8e80-aeb8198da9ac"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"mention","attrs":{"id":"5ffc6569f7ea2a0107e76107","text":"@Marta Turesko","accessLevel":"","localId":"0c843aba-83e4-4807-ac21-7c3db3a47fd7"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"hardBreak"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"hardBreak"}]}]}
